title: Sofia with an F
description:
Sofia With an F (aka Sofia Franklyn) has the tea on EVERYTHING, and pulls no punches! She grew up in Utah near Lala, and spills plenty of tea on people they both know (not necessarily from Utah). Sofia also talks about betrayal, cheating, being arrested by the cops, and starting her own podcast after “Call Me Daddy” imploded! Plus, Lala shares details about filming the #PumpRules reunion, and answers some voicemails about mental health and motherhood.
